          >? If you have ideas or thoughts or if you're going through a similar
          journey, I'd love <a
            href="mailto:spencer@spencer.place?subject=MAKING A LIVING DOING WHAT YOU LOVE IS HARD!!!"
            >to chat</a
          >.
        </p>
      </details>
